<template>

</template>

<script>
  import { Icon } from "@iconify/vue";
  let _uid = 0;

  export default {
    data() {
      _uid += 1;
      return {
        isOpen: false,
        uid: `collapse${_uid}`,
      };
    },

    methods: {
      toggleAccordion() {
        this.isOpen = !this.isOpen;
      },
    },
    components: {
      Icon,
    },
  };
</script>
